tre choix que de conclure un accord dont les conséquences, au fil des mois, bouleverseront le destin de nos trois personnages.","Paris 1941. François Mercier is an ordinary man whose only goal is to start a family with Blanche, the woman he loves. François works for Mr. Haffmann, a talented Jewish jeweler. Under the German occupation, the employer and employee are forced to strike a deal which, over the following months, will upend the fate of our three protagonists."],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
